&lt;p&gt;We are looking to recruit enthusiastic nurses who are committed to providing an excellent standard of care, in a considerate and compassionate manner. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;This fast-paced 32 bedded surgical ward cares for colorectal and upper GI patients, as well as patients discharged from ICU. We are also a tertiary referral service for bariatric patients, and are equipped to handle the most complex of cases.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;You will be supported by our team of senior nurses, CNSs and clinical educators in gaining new skills and furthering your career.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Karen Santamaria-Woods, Ward Manager: 0208 725 3403 or e-mail at Karen.santamariawoods@stgeorges.nhs.uk&lt;/p&gt;
